## FEATURES

• **UNLIMITED OPENS** – No keys needed, no limits
• **ALL CASES** – Every CS2 case ever released
• **REAL DROP RATES** – Same odds as official game
• **INVENTORY SYSTEM** – Save your unboxed items
• **STATS TRACKING** – See your luck over time
• **BATCH OPENING** – Open 10, 100, or 1000 at once
• **SOUND EFFECTS** – Authentic case opening sounds
• **SKIN PREVIEW** – Inspect items in 3D
• **NO CS2 REQUIRED** – Works standalone

